"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:3.1.2.6\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">3.1.2.6</span> 標題：門檻（threshold, doorsill）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： סַף</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： saf)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg19:27\">JDG 19:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:17\">1KI 14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek40:6\">EZK 40:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek40:6\">EZK 40:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek40:7\">EZK 40:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek41:16\">EZK 41:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek41:16\">EZK 41:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek43:8\">EZK 43:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek43:8\">EZK 43:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:14\">ZEP 2:14</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מִפְתָּן</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： miftan)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam5:4\">1SA 5:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam5:5\">1SA 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek9:3\">EZK 9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:4\">EZK 10:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:18\">EZK 10:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:2\">EZK 46:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek47:1\">EZK 47:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:9\">ZEP 1:9</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： χελώνις</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： chelōnis)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt14:15\">JDT 14:15</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0406_threshold_hant.jpg\" alt=\"門檻\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">門檻 (© Dietmar Rabich, CC BY-SA 4.0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>門檻位於門框的底部（參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.1.2 門、門口 (door, doorway)&lt;REALIA:3.1.2&gt;</a> ），水平放置在地面上，通常用石頭做成。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>如果沒有「門檻」的專用名稱，或者人們一般不理解這個詞，翻譯者可能需要使用一個描述性短語；例如，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek9:3\">EZK 9:3</a> 可譯為「門打開的地方」（<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 直譯）。</p>\n<p>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:9\">ZEP 1:9</a> ：在這節經文中，原文字面意為「所有跳過（或譯：跳上）門檻的人」的短語有些含糊，並且在不同譯本中的譯法也很不同。該詞可能是指非利士人的宗教習俗，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam5:4\">1SA 5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam5:5\">1SA 5:5</a> 敘述了這個習俗的起源。為了反映這一點，<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Contemporary English Version\">CEV</abbr> 譯為“worshipers of pagan gods”（「敬拜異教神明的人」），並添加了一個腳註。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Century Version\">NCV</abbr> 更加具體，譯為“those who worship Dagon”（「那些敬拜大袞的人」），但沒有添加腳註。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"French Common Language Version (Bible en français courant)\">FRCL</abbr> 提供了另一種處理方法，將其擴展譯為：「所有像異教徒一樣跳過聖殿門檻的人。」<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"French Common Language Version (Bible en français courant)\">FRCL</abbr> 在腳註中包含了另一種譯法：「所有登上（神聖的）平臺的人。」另參《〈那鴻書〉、〈哈巴谷書〉和〈西番雅書〉手冊》（<em>A Handbook on The Books of Nahum, Habakkuk, and Zephaniah</em> ）第152—153頁的討論。</p>\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/OAI-0030_threshold_hant.png\" alt=\"門柱和門楣\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">門柱和門楣 (Image generated by ChatGPT using OpenAI technology)</figcaption></figure>\n            <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt14:15\">JDT 14:15</a> 中的希臘文<em>chelōnis</em> 意思比較模糊。<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New Jerusalem Bible (1985)\">NJB</abbr> 譯作“threshold”（「門檻」），這也是利德爾—斯科特（Liddell&amp;Scott）給出的定義。我們從<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jdt13:9\">JDT 13:9</a> 中知道，友弟德把敖羅斐乃的屍體從床上翻下來，也就是說屍體是躺在地上的。因此，許多譯本在《次經‧猶滴傳》14:15（《思》《友弟德傳》）中把<em>chelōnis</em> 譯為「地板」（“floor”；<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"Italian Common Language Version\">ITCL</abbr> 、<abbr class=\"thlex-abbr\" title=\"New American Bible (1970)\">NAB</abbr> ），這種譯法似乎更可取。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
